30 seconds to get pet and buffs is all im alowing. This will make the casters think of whats more important buffs or mana. Pets are expensive as they should be... they will have to consider if its worth the mana. - THis rule is Firm<br>
<br>
So Enchanters...Bards... Dont just sit there and sing it...move your a$$ and bring it..(no pun intened) <br>
